title: Beauty.and.the.Geek.AU.s06e01.PDTV.x264.Hector.mp4
description: The Geeks have hit the jackpot when they find themselves in Las Vegas, coupled up with US Beauties consisting of models, pageant winners and beauty queens. In this episode, the Geeks are dared to bare all in a Vegas strip show and the beauties will be tested on all things Australian. The winning team will gain immunity but one couple will be eliminated. Plus, a bombshell will change everything!
